---
title: "AI as Team Amplifier, Not Team Replacement"
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph BEFORE["BEFORE AI"]
        direction TB
        B1["👤 👤 👤 👤 👤"]
        B2["Team of 5 = Output X"]
        B1 --- B2
    end

    BEFORE -- "AI joins\nthe team" --> AFTER

    subgraph AFTER["WITH AI"]
        direction TB
        A1["👤🤖 👤🤖 👤🤖 👤🤖 👤🤖"]
        A2["Same Team of 5 = Output X × Y"]
        A1 --- A2
    end

    NOTE["Same people, amplified capability.\nAI multiplies what teams can deliver,\nit does not reduce who delivers."]

    AFTER --- NOTE

    style BEFORE fill:#F0F4F8,color:#1B3A5C,stroke:#2E75B6
    style AFTER fill:#FFF8E8,color:#1B3A5C,stroke:#D4A84B
    style NOTE fill:#fff,color:#2D2D2D,stroke:#ccc
    style B1 fill:#F0F4F8,color:#2E75B6,stroke:none
    style B2 fill:#F0F4F8,color:#1B3A5C,stroke:none
